             was indicted for <rs id="t18021027-64-off342" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-64-off342" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-64-off342" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18021027-64-cd343" type="crimeDate">14th of Oc<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180210270033"></xptr>tober</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-64-off342 t18021027-64-cd343"></join>, a cord, value 1d. a mat, value 1s. and 112lb. weight of snuff, value 12l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18021027-64-victim578" type="victimName">
                           Martin 
                           Pearkes
                        <interp inst="t18021027-64-victim578" type="surname" value="Pearkes"></interp>
